George Baker (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Baker_(actor) 0 For the Bengali actor-cum-politician, see George Baker. George Morris Baker, MBE (1 April 1931 – 7 October 2011) was an English actor and writer. He was best known for portraying Tiberius in I, Claudius, and Inspector Wexford in The Ruth Rendell Mysteries. For the_Bengali_actor-cum-politician , see George_Baker .
